  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/20dce6b7fd873ba43bbcb43a5223f19d.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/20dce6b7fd873ba43bbcb43a5223f19d.webm?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/20dce6b7fd873ba43bbcb43a5223f19d.mp4?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Welcome to the exciting world of Sky Sojourn!</strong> <br>In this adventure game you will play as Steve, a brave adventurer who finds himself on a remote deserted island full of mysteries and riddles.<br><br>Your task is to climb up a variety of floating islands. To reach the top, you will have to overcome many exciting obstacles. Be ready for unusual challenges!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/487114073ebe6aa5c23ba77c491e934c.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/487114073ebe6aa5c23ba77c491e934c.webm?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/487114073ebe6aa5c23ba77c491e934c.mp4?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The peculiarity of the game are pushing spheres and elevators that will help you climb to the top! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/c1f987d99e68cc9150475736fd6e84c5.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/c1f987d99e68cc9150475736fd6e84c5.webm?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/c1f987d99e68cc9150475736fd6e84c5.mp4?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The higher you go up the more painful it is to fall as there are no saves in the game and if you fall from a great height the game will be over.</strong> But the main thing is not to give up and you will definitely be able to overcome all the obstacles and find out what is at the top!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/4dd1bd78620ea22a6b995f8d110245f8.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/4dd1bd78620ea22a6b995f8d110245f8.webm?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/4dd1bd78620ea22a6b995f8d110245f8.mp4?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/92d7f75cb70c2acbacb6e8ecd05ba40e.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=538 height=101 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/92d7f75cb70c2acbacb6e8ecd05ba40e.webm?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/20dce6b7fd873ba43bbcb43a5223f19d.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/20dce6b7fd873ba43bbcb43a5223f19d.webm?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/20dce6b7fd873ba43bbcb43a5223f19d.mp4?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Welcome to the exciting world of Sky Sojourn!</strong> <br>In this adventure game you will play as Steve, a brave adventurer who finds himself on a remote deserted island full of mysteries and riddles.<br><br>Your task is to climb up a variety of floating islands. To reach the top, you will have to overcome many exciting obstacles. Be ready for unusual challenges!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/487114073ebe6aa5c23ba77c491e934c.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/487114073ebe6aa5c23ba77c491e934c.webm?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/487114073ebe6aa5c23ba77c491e934c.mp4?t=1702330113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The peculiarity of the game are pushing spheres and elevators that will help you climb to the top! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543940/extras/c1f987d99e68cc9150475736fd6e84c5.poster.avif?t=1702330113\" width=800 height=2